00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:15,480
 I'll tell you how it happened.

139
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:19,080
 It happened because a young man, a young leader,

140
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:22,280
 someone like you in their 20s and 30s

