00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:03,900
 And listen, they were good, like really good.

788
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:06,380
 Like they'd won state the year before kinda good

789
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:08,780
 and played in a different district altogether than us,

790
00:35:08,780 --> 00:35:09,940
 and yet in this moment,

791
00:35:09,940 --> 00:35:13,340
 they were coming to play against us, and we were bad.

792
00:35:13,340 --> 00:35:14,340
 And I'm not being modest.

793
00:35:14,340 --> 00:35:15,540
 Like we were really bad.

794
00:35:15,540 --> 00:35:18,060
 We were not in any way whatsoever

795
00:35:18,060 --> 00:35:19,860
 comparable for the competition.

796
00:35:19,860 --> 00:35:21,780
 And yet in this moment, our coach knew,

797
00:35:21,780 --> 00:35:24,380
 hey, I'm gonna give you good courage.

798
00:35:24,380 --> 00:35:26,020
 I'm gonna train you, I'm gonna prepare you,

799
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:27,220
 we're gonna practice hard.

800
00:35:27,220 --> 00:35:30,180
 You're gonna have every reason to step into that fray

801
00:35:30,180 --> 00:35:32,100
 and fight as well as possible.

802
00:35:32,100 --> 00:35:34,000
 And yet he also knew, though you have courage,

803
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:36,540
 you need some confidence to boost that courage.

804
00:35:36,540 --> 00:35:37,980
 You get a little shot in the arm.

805
00:35:37,980 --> 00:35:42,140
 And so he walked into that meeting and he gave us a speech,

806
00:35:42,140 --> 00:35:47,720
 the likes of which I dream about to this day.

