00:35:49,720 --> 00:35:54,240
 It fills my bones as I prepare to preach.

808
00:35:54,240 --> 00:35:55,960
 You know, it's like that kind of moment.

809
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:57,560
 It was so motivating.

810
00:35:57,560 --> 00:36:00,840
 It roused my inner man and it led me forth

811
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:03,720
 into the throes of battle to be utterly defeated.

