00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:11,900
 but you also need good reason for courage.

815
00:36:11,900 --> 00:36:13,760
 You need some confidence beneath it.

816
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:17,320
 Timothy needs the same from Paul.

817
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:20,400
 So Paul, he writes this pump up speech.

818
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:24,640
 He gets so engulfed by all that he's sharing.

819
00:36:24,640 --> 00:36:26,800
 And the reason why is because he wants Timothy to know,

820
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:30,220
 hey, true courage finds its confidence in Christ.

821
00:36:30,220 --> 00:36:33,000
 True courage, it finds its confidence in Christ.

822
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:34,520
 It doesn't find its confidence in anything else.

823
00:36:34,520 --> 00:36:36,280
 It doesn't find its confidence in your ability.

824
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:39,360
 It doesn't find its confidence in your social status.

825
00:36:39,360 --> 00:36:42,360
 It doesn't find its confidence in what people think of you

826
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:46,640
 or how well you're regarded, what your reputation is online.

827
00:36:46,640 --> 00:36:49,760
 It doesn't find confidence in anything but him.

828
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:53,040
 And the reason we know that is he gives us four reasons

829
00:36:53,040 --> 00:36:56,240
 within these four verses for that confidence.

830
00:36:56,240 --> 00:36:57,760
 He tells us first and foremost in verse nine

831
00:36:57,760 --> 00:37:00,960
 that Jesus is the one who calls and saves.

832
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:03,880
 He's the one who calls and saves.

833
00:37:03,880 --> 00:37:04,720
 Like, I love it.

834
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:07,040
 None of us were looking for Jesus when he found us.

835
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:09,440
 None of us.

836
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:11,640
 Like, think about where you were when he found you.

837
00:37:11,640 --> 00:37:12,540
 I know where I was.

838
00:37:12,540 --> 00:37:16,160
 Like, I was at this cheesy little youth group conference

839
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:18,000
 out in Arlington, Texas.

840
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:19,560
 And as I sat in this room,

841
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:23,840
 it was this overly dramatic skit from stage

