00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:27,120
 that absolutely plucked my heartstrings

843
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:29,160
 and compelled my faith.

844
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:31,680
 And I look back on that and I'm like, oh my gosh,

845
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:34,680
 like, that is the most cringe-worthy skit ever.

846
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:37,840
 And yet it was through that thing that Jesus decided,

847
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:38,840
 yep, you're mine, come on.

848
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:42,320
 Like, he used that because he doesn't need anything else.

849
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:43,520
 He can do whatever he wants

