00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:16,320
 but by his own purpose and grace."

863
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:19,920
 Meaning, listen, someone's salvation does not depend

864
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:22,360
 on your ability to get the sales pitch right.

865
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:25,240
 Some of you need to hear that.

866
00:38:25,240 --> 00:38:28,880
 Like someone's salvation, it does not depend

