00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:53,560
 "Hey man, their soul is worth more than your approval.

898
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:56,160
 "So tell them about me."

899
00:39:56,160 --> 00:39:59,440
 That's the third reason.

