00:41:04,240 --> 00:41:07,640
 and then ultimately beating back all shame forever

926
00:41:07,640 --> 00:41:09,120
 for those that would believe in him

927
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:11,320
 just so we could know about each other.

928
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:15,440
 Do you hear how ludicrous that is?

929
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,920
 That's not what he's come to do.

