00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:28,000
 He died so people would know him,

936
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:30,560
 walk with him, love him, relate to him.

937
00:41:31,560 --> 00:41:32,800
 And I probably shouldn't say this,

938
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:34,200
 but if that's your strategy,

939
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:36,160
 you should ask yourself the question,

940
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:38,800
 how well do you know him

941
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,240
 or do you just know about him?

942
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:45,400
 We have good reason for confidence, friends.

943
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:48,600
 God has given us a spirit of courage

