00:43:14,520 --> 00:43:19,520
 And I'm not witty enough and I'm not learned enough

974
00:43:19,520 --> 00:43:21,840
 and I'm not smart enough and I'm not enough.

975
00:43:21,840 --> 00:43:24,280
 Like that's the bottom line is I'm just not enough.

976
00:43:24,280 --> 00:43:26,120
 And so Jesus, you've got to find someone else.

977
00:43:26,120 --> 00:43:28,400
 Like I trust that you will do that.

