00:44:18,640 --> 00:44:20,360
 He moved from heaven to earth

993
00:44:20,360 --> 00:44:22,840
 and he navigated all the complexities

994
00:44:22,840 --> 00:44:27,760
 and all the difficulties and all the challenges

