00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:33,760
 And we were ashamed of our sin

998
00:44:33,760 --> 00:44:36,400
 and yet Jesus was not ashamed of you at all.

999
00:44:36,400 --> 00:44:39,080
 He lived uncensored for you.

