00:45:46,920 --> 00:45:51,120
 And so he had confidence to come and to get you.

1021
00:45:51,120 --> 00:45:55,320
 Jesus knew when his time had come

1022
00:45:55,320 --> 00:45:58,640
 that his turn was then and he raced into it.

1023
00:45:58,640 --> 00:46:02,640
 Paul, Paul knew when his time had come

1024
00:46:02,640 --> 00:46:07,280
 and when his turn was now and he raced into it.

