00:46:07,280 --> 00:46:08,680
 The same was true for Timothy.

1026
00:46:08,680 --> 00:46:11,320
 The question that I just wanna leave you with is,

1027
00:46:11,320 --> 00:46:14,960
 do you believe your time is now and your turn has come?

1028
00:46:14,960 --> 00:46:18,040
 And will you race into it as well?

1029
00:46:18,040 --> 00:46:21,040
 Let me pray that you would.

